name: This Is The Air That I Breathe
chorusText:
You are the air I breathe
Your Holy pre—sence
Living   -- in me
This is my daily bread
This is my daily bread
You’re every w—ord

1 of 2
And I……I’m desperate for You
And I……I’m desperate for You
And I……I’m lost without You
And I……I’m lost without You
2 of 2
